	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00">Since you were cool about the
scallop,<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /> I left you a cool recipe
in return.
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />The <colour id="1" />pearls<colour id="65535" /> you need for that recipe
