them on the ocean floor.
I keep my eyes open for them too,<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
and I might even trade you for a
scallop if I find one.
Forget "give and take."<delay8 /> <anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />This is called
give and GIVE.<delay20 /> That's how we all
win,<delay8 /> ya dig?
Now, if you don't mind, <delay8 />I'd like to lay
some truth on you<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />the deep kind.</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Feel this<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00">Yep. Today is a gooood day.</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Wrap your noodle around that.</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Stick that in your skillet and let
